      1204,
      267
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Xét tam giác vuông $A'AB$: $AA' = \\sqrt{A'B^2 - AB^2} = \\sqrt{3a^2 - a^2} = a\\sqrt{2}$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      202,
      277,
      887,
      365
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Thể tích: $V = S_{ABC} \\cdot AA' = \\frac{1}{2}a^2 \\cdot a\\sqrt{2} = \\frac{a^3\\sqrt{2}}{2}$."
  },
